<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent20441e744cc64b7684accb1a3ede2478">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Rotherham Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=1066"/>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>The Rotherham NHS Foundation Trust manages services based at Rotherham Hospital, Rotherham Community Health Centre, The Park Rehabillitaion Centre atÂ Badsley Moor Lane, and Othalmology services at Barnsley Hospital.</strong></p>
<p>The Rotherham Hospital site is set in leafy suburbs, 1 mile from the M1, 6 miles from Sheffield and close to Doncaster. We provide all major outpatient &amp; inpatient specialities.</p>
<p>The modern Rotherham Hospital site provides a range of hospital based Medical, Surgical, Paediatric and Obstetric &amp; Gynaecological services. The excellent and modern facilities include:</p>
<ul>
<li>500 inpatient beds </li>
<li>Intensive Therapy and Coronary Care Units </li>
<li>Cardiac Catheterisation Suite </li>
<li>Breast Screening Suite </li>
<li>Endoscopy Unit </li>
<li>Day Surgery Unit </li>
<li>Theatre Assessment Unit </li>
<li>Stroke Unit </li>
</ul>
<p>The clinical services are supported by comprehensive pathology, medical physics and imaging services, including state of the art MRI and CT facilities.</p></div>
</div>
